#. type: Plain text
#: source/server_admin/topics/login-settings/forgot-password.adoc:6
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"If you enable it, users are able to reset their credentials if they forget their password or lose their OTP generator.\n"
"Go to the `Realm Settings` left menu item, and click on the `Login` tab.  Switch on the `Forgot Password` switch.\n"
msgstr ""

