#. type: Plain text
#: source/server_admin/topics/login-settings/forgot-password.adoc:23
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"The text sent in the email is completely configurable. You just need to extend or edit the theme associated with it.\n"
"See the link:{developerguide_link}[{developerguide_name}] for more information.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: source/server_admin/topics/login-settings/forgot-password.adoc:28
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"When the user clicks on the email link, they will be asked to update their password, and, if they have an OTP generator\n"
"set up, they will also be asked to reconfigure this as well.  Depending on the security requirements of your organization\n"
"you may not want users to be able to reset their OTP generator through email.  You can change this behavior by\n"
"going to the `Authentication` left menu item, clicking on the `Flows` tab, and selecting the `Reset Credentials` flow:\n"
msgstr ""

